thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOxJd5V.jpg&h=fe7f7cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀 荃葵青街坊<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"做好封鐵準備，到時應該點走"},{"pid":"7d4c593e1dabc575edfb6cdcf13cd45a7c0f59ae","tid":1501064,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e15329d96391cfefdec1f5423a9bd011b5ad6f","tid":1501064,"uid":25533,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"去和你飛啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"青馬大橋+汀九橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74530acd1f911457f51f421423d2c6f45041b5d","tid":1501064,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"宜家變了集會<br />\n<br />\nFrom Facebook <br />\n各位，<br />\n<br />\n8月25日荃葵青遊行籌委於今日下午正式收到警方就825荃葵青遊行的反對通知書，只批准於荃灣公園舉辦集會。<br />\n<br />\n籌委現計劃於八月二十三日傍晚6時30分於葵涌廣場外之空地召開記者招待會交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉行日期：2019年8月25日<br />\n時間：1500<br />\n地點：荃灣公園<br />\n<br />\n聚焦目標：<br />\n1. 五大訴求（撤回逃犯條例修訂草案、撤銷所有義士控罪、徹查並追究所有黑警開槍血腥鎮壓之責任、撤回暴動定性、我要真&middot;雙普選）<br />\n2. 要求全面追究參與警黑合作、發動及參與721元朗及805荃灣恐怖襲擊之恐怖份子的所有刑事責任<br />\n3. 要求全面追究涉事插贓嫁禍、妨礙司法公正之警員責任<br />\n4. 抗議警察偽裝示威者，及其發動的一切暴力行為"},{"pid":"ec4a6e0aeb8a9a8a1d24cf0fd8d02a6e5536c6c5","tid":1501064,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc27b9cf133c303b05599665624c8e841d0f1fff","tid":1501064,"uid":51913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbeda0c7517af96163011cf566f640128ef95bca","tid":1501064,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"明天見呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddb7c5274a96982aef6e68