ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"明明一直都係講緊825荃葵青<br />\n唔知點解經過幾次和理非活動之後<br />\n香港人既抗爭熱潮冷卻咗落嚟<br />\n我哋近1000個手足被捕<br />\n3人盲眼<br />\n1人腳部被斬至永久傷殘<br />\n1人被斬至肺功能受損<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日忽然見到好多帶風向post<br />\n話聽日要入機場<br />\n<br />\n好老實講<br />\n經過2星期和理非<br />\n個社會好似唔記得晒警察 政府點殘暴對待市民<br />\n連政府高官 權貴eg 曾俊華都吹和風<br />\n想香港人妥協<br />\n<br />\n所以我好多謝今日觀塘手足既付出<br />\n將革命重新延續落去<br />\n聽日對運動嚟講亦係一個關鍵<br />\n究竟革命能否延續<br />\n就睇各位放唔放棄"},{"pid":"41fd18fa26d6b4c04794cf4fb4f403d30d68b249","tid":1501064,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8003cb8bbcfb3e991dd8e921addf99342e60dd87","tid":1501064,"uid":103649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"665e7638b66c33d22a1207b6a59c9d93bd9f6528","tid":1501064,"uid":285744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"85d3f061945f80812f289a02b7fd550f1641221a","tid":1501064,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b919ffc1d0ab8e9db70477795c1b6af5bf1e8415","tid":1501064,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3b4ed58f88775875a74baba8c10c84255326860","tid":1501064,"uid":6308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"4f87f10a9d045bbfcd9629195d225c4964afa893","tid":1501064,"uid":64594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a55430d422f885cde149cdc5c639f59635930cf0","tid":1501064,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a69c5d4a73371904e1ede703f3db608583ff931","tid":1501064,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"推